name: No Inspiration Today
description: circumstances continue to force to do something even though sometimes the condition of the heart and mind is uncertain. Yes, this is my work where when I made it, I was in a state of many thoughts making my heart and brain keep colliding so that my imagination/inspiration disappeared but my conscience continued to keep working while logic forced me not to. Continuing to move and work even when things are not okay is the end of the choice that results in the work "No Inspiration Today"
